channel.title: How do I turn on my No-IP?
channel.description:
This may sound like a VERY dumb question because I am new to server making.
But, how do i turn on my NO-IP?

item.title: How do I turn on my No-IP?
item.dc:creator: @burnout burnout
item.description:
@burnout wrote:

you have msn messenger dont you?[br][br][size=1]Posted on: February 12, 2008, 09:02:08 PM[/size][hr]this goes in compiler you ming have to replace the 3 in this

if exist "C:/program files/java/jdk1.6.0_03/bin/javac.exe" goto java6

with a 4, and you have to replace both of them as theres 2 lines like this one in it

[code]@echo off
COLOR F0
Title Compiler
echo *******************************************************************************
echo * Compile Complete by Burnout *
echo * *
echo * specially created for NOOBS!!! *
echo * *
echo *******************************************************************************
echo Checking Java version…
echo.

:checkjava
echo 06
if exist “C:/program files/java/jdk1.6.0_03/bin/javac.exe” goto java6

:java6
echo.
echo compiling…
echo java version: 1.6.0_03
echo.
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_03\bin/javac.exe” *.java -nowarn *.java
goto end

:end
echo.
echo Complete!
echo.
set recomp=
set /p recomp= press enter to close
goto close

:close
echo.
echo closing compiler…
[/code]
